answers.text: I have chronic and mental health conditions which have been affected by all of this. My hospital appointments have been cancelled so I am left in pain, we have lost loved ones and it’s affected my mental wellbeing. There has been positives but I feel that it has been very up and down and at times extremely difficult. I’m lucky to have a good support system at home, others who don’t would definitely struggle with conditions like mine if not in a safe space.
